export function humanize(raw: string) {
  const titleCase = raw
    .replace(/_/g, " ")
    .replace(/([a-z0-9])([A-Z])/g, "$1 $2")
    .replace(/\s+/g, " ")
    .replace(/^./, (m) => m.toUpperCase());
  return LABEL_TRANSLATIONS[titleCase] || titleCase;
}
